<ab facs="#facs_214_r1l33">anders <expan>fürgeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / <expan>dan<ex>n</ex></expan> ſich das verloffen hab . darümb Jr Jm </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_214_r1l34"><expan>verſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt / <expan>denſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> brief Er vns fürbraht 
